t.
It=E2=80=99s a very awkward bankruptcy. Ray and FTX=E2=80=99s bankruptcy te=
am are in charge of rounding up assets that they can use to pay back custom=
ers, and conceptually the assets fall into four big categories:
=09More-or-less liquid normal stuff. Cash, Bitcoin, etc.=C2=A0=09Illiquid v=
enture-y stuff. Stakes in startups that Bankman-Fried liked, stakes in vent=
