uch is owed to customers, but in any case nobody=C2=A0thinks that these nor=
mal assets add up to anything close to enough to pay back customers.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">So that leaves the third and fourth categories=
, FTX=E2=80=99s operating business and its associated tokens. How much are =
these things worth? FTX=E2=80=99s current and former=C2=A0CEOs seem to have=
