<ul style=3D"list-style-type: disc; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;">=
=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Bankman-Fried seems to think that FTX=
=E2=80=99s business, and its=C2=A0FTT, SRM, etc. tokens, are very valuable.=
 That=E2=80=99s why he was shopping them to potential investors before fili=
