=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Ray obviously disagrees. =E2=80=9CNeve=
r in my career have I seen such a complete failure of corporate controls,=
=E2=80=9D etc.: He thinks that the FTX business was terribly run and not tr=
